results.title: Live Laugh Love Sticker For Car Window, Bumper, or Laptop. Free Shipping!
results.description:
This high quality sticker will look great on you car window, bumper, side panel, or laptop!

All stickers are die cut in a high quality vinyl film designed to last up to 7 years outdoors! 

To install:

1. Once your sticker is removed from package, lay it on a flat surface like a counter or tabletop.

2. Gently rub your hand a crossed the top of the transfer tap insuring it sticks to the sticker below.

3. Once the transfer tape is secure to the sticker below, gently peel the tape back lifting the sticker from the backing paper. It's important to do this slowly so that no details get left behind and there are no rips.

4. Take your sticker to a previously cleaned surface on your vehicles window, bumper, or side panel. Lay the sticker on your desired surface and again start rubbing the transfer tape to make sure the sticker takes to the surface. During this step it's recommended that you use a credit card to apply extra force.

5. Peel transfer tape back. If you performed all the steps up until now correctly, your sticker will be resting on your desired surface. If you see any bubbles at this point do not panic as they will disappear in the near future.

If you have any problems with your order, including install, please feel free to reach out to us 24/7. Returns are accepted on all orders up to 30 days after delivery. Generally speaking, guidelines do not mean much to us and our business transaction with you is not complete until your satisfied.
